{"tid":515660,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"細路插隊去廁所係理所當然？","createTime":"2017-12-31T15:46:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-31T17:04:13.000Z","uid":119174,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"7cff05ac68e37475e061a2f627ab521884d05833","tid":515660,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T15:46:17.000Z","msg":"事緣今日去某商場女廁 女廁排長龍係人都知 <br />\n排排下有一對講普通話既母子插隊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：我<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：個阿媽<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 排喺我前面既女仔<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：（行到隊前）哎呀小朋友忍不住呀 先讓他去吧<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：那邊有殘廁<br />\n然後個母子出左去睇殘廁 但之後又入番黎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：鎖了 <br />\n結果個阿媽直接去空既廁格 比排我前面既女仔更早去廁格<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔俾個細路仔去又好衰 俾個細路仔去就係對排隊既人唔公平<br />\n細路仔唔忍得我明白 真係隨時瀨俾你睇<br />\n但係係咪真係要做到插隊 殘廁通常都唔洗點排隊<br />\n整件事對我無乜害 因為我都可以忍 而且之前我都有讓過妹妹去先 但重點係我身後都有好多小妹妹排隊等緊 無一個好似佢咁插隊<br />\n教育真係從細教起 父母就係身教 小朋友既第一個老師<br />\n我見個細路仔起碼都有四歲 作為父母係咪應該教一教自己個仔唔好忍一急就要講？ 否則我相信佢都唔洗做到插隊 係咪俾你去之後要講唔好意思/對唔住/唔該曬你？<br />\n不過俾佢插一插隊就成功 唔怪之得咁多大陸人咁鐘意插隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多野都係要從細教 唔係話&rsquo;細個邊明邊識咁多 佢地大個自然識啦&lsquo; 就唔教<br />\n<br />\n你地又會唔會讓小朋友去先？有無試過因為個父母無禮貌而拒絕？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd97b59baaa749dcb01464f42effefba6dcb2df","tid":515660,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T15:47:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b3f629f21fe99bcfc85d8f291001f6642a40a0d","tid":515660,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T15:53:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"346a427fe6a387c177567607324b9de513575976","tid":515660,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T16:06:56.000Z","msg":"除夕無人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f65fed5b942e5be40eca27c8b1c3b0e633744b71","tid":515660,"uid":61752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T16:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bde1d415862e42da51ccf11e56ad3ddde005713","tid":515660,"uid":119174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T16:59:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0251d279af4508da3695256dfabde2ca06e1f0cf","tid":515660,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T17:04:13.000Z","msg":"屌 你可以點姐<br />\n你出聲人地又話鳩你唔讓<br />\n呢啲野睇開啲啦<br />\n重係咁推推推 根本buy你同唔buy你都得<br />\n你又唔係急到賴既 咪讓囉<br />\n你都有做過細路既時候 咁執著做乜"}]}